Diabetes

Diabetes Prevalence by State

diabetes <-
  read_csv("diabetes.csv") %>%
  na.omit %>%
  filter(
    STATE != "Puerto Rico"
  )

data("state_laea")
state_laea$STATE[1] = "Arizona"
state_laea$STATE[2] = "Arkansas"

diabetes_by_state <-
  diabetes %>%
  inner_join(state_laea, by = c("STATE" = "STATE")) %>%
  st_as_sf()

tm_shape(diabetes_by_state) +
tm_polygons(col = "PERCENT", legend.hist = TRUE, border.col = "white") +
tm_layout(main.title = "Percent Population (> 20 Years Old) Diagnosed as Diabetic", main.title.size = 1, legend.outside = TRUE, legend.title.color = "white", legend.title.size = 0.0001, legend.hist.width = 1)

Obesity

Obesity Prevalence by State

obesity <-
  read_csv("obesity.csv")

obesity_by_state <-
  obesity %>%
  inner_join(state_laea, by = c("STATE" = "STATE")) %>%
  st_as_sf()

tm_shape(obesity_by_state) +
tm_polygons(col = "PERCENT", legend.hist = TRUE, border.col = "white") +
tm_layout(main.title = "Percent Prevalence of Obesity", main.title.size = 1, legend.outside = TRUE, legend.title.color = "white", legend.title.size = 0.0001, legend.hist.width = 1)
